                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d79">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 80.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Pelting</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-11-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 23, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Yesterday China made through me direct overtures to Japan for peace; basis,
                    independence Korea; war indemnity. Unless peace made ask Secretary of the Navy
                    strengthen <hi rend="italic">Monocacy</hi> crew fifty men for service
                    Peking.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
